Cha helps reduce innitial resists on all mental spells(even nukes)<br>
Cha helps Charm last longer and break early less<br>
Cha helps vendor sales<br>
Cha helps for faction (my own observances not proven in any way)<br>
Cha is the secondary check for the Lull Series, if the spell fails, it then checks Cha, if you pass the check the mob does not agro you. If you fail it goes to a 3rd check to see if any other Non lulled agro you as well.<br>
Cha determines the amount of agro you recieve on failed spells, and im a firm believe it even works on successful spells<br>
